<A>__{at first we should not realize we are near a building of any kind. we open on a wide angle on the dead sea from a stunning pov. crane down to reveal the silhouette of ramirez smoking a cigarette. we now see that his nose is exactly that of carlos. he has just a bit of dark circles left under his eyes, just enough to make him seem moody. he tosses the cigarette and turns to enter a room. now we see that this is a deserted barracks pock marked with artillery shells and machine gun bullet holes from past wars.}
